  "texts": [
    "A perspective article proposed an MBE conceptual framework for CHD [6], in which similarity analysis is used to generate a library of \"approximate matches.\"",
    "However, they did not provide any technical solution for this framework.",
    "The challenge in applying PSNs in a real clinical setting is, first of all, to assess the distance between patients with complex conditions such as CHD in a computable way.",
    "However, mimicking clinical analogy reasoning is not a simple math formula based on various patients' attributes.",
    "The structuremapping theory in cognitive science argues that advanced cognitive functions are involved in the analysis of relationship similarity above attribute similarity [37]."
